column1: # target       : target A used in single or double ratio
# singleR_A_c12_src      : single ratio of target A_SRC / C12_SRC
# singleR_per_nucleon      : single ratio of target A(SRC/MF) per nucleon
# singleR_per_nucleon_err  : uncertainty in single ratio per nucleon
# singleR_per_nucleus      : single ratio of target A(SRC/MF) per nucleus
# singleR_per_nucleus_err  : uncertainty in single ratio per nucleus
# doubleR_per_nucleon      : double ratio of target A(SRC/MF) relative to C12 (SRC/MF)
# doubleR_per_nucleus      : double ratio of target A(SRC/MF) relative to C12 (SRC/MF)
# N: Z: A      : # of neutrons (N): protons(Z): nucleons (A): for target A
